<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Free Roof Inspection - Storm Damage Help</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: #f8f9fa;
      color: #333;
    }
    header {
      background-color: #004466;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .hero {
      padding: 2rem;
      background-color: #e9f5ff;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .hero h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    .cta-button {
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .section {
      padding: 2rem;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: auto;
    }
    .contact-form {
      background: #fff;
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    input, textarea, select {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 0.75rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    footer {
      background-color: #004466;
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>[Your Logo]</h1>
    <p>Worried About Storm Damage? We've Got You Covered.</p>
  </header>

  <div class="hero">
    <h2>Free Roof Inspections in Your Area</h2>
    <p>Recent storms brought 1–2" hail and 80+ MPH winds. Your roof could be damaged—get it checked for FREE!</p>
    <button class="cta-button" onclick="document.getElementById('contact').scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' });">Book My Free Inspection</button>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h3>What We Do</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>✔ Roof Repairs & Replacements</li>
      <li>✔ Free Storm Damage Inspections</li>
      <li>✔ Help with Insurance Claims</li>
      <li>✔ Fast, Local Service</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h3>Contact a Sales Rep</h3>
    <div class="contact-form" id="contact">
      <form action="https://formspree.io/f/xnnvojbe" method="POST">
        <label for="name">Name</label>
        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required />

        <label for="phone">Phone Number</label>
        <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" required />

        <label for="email">Email</label>
        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required />

        <label for="address">Address</label>
        <input type="text" id="address" name="address" required />

        <label for="contact-method">Preferred Contact Method</label>
        <select id="contact-method" name="contact-method">
          <option value="phone">Phone</option>
          <option value="email">Email</option>
          <option value="text">Text</option>
        </select>

        <label for="message">Message (optional)</label>
        <textarea id="message" name="message"></textarea>

        <input type="hidden" name="_next" value="https://yourwebsite.com/thank-you.html" />

        <button type="submit" class="cta-button">Schedule Now</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <p>📞 [Phone Number] | 🌐 [Website] | 📧 [Email Address]</p>
    <p>📍 [Business Address] | 🔒 100% Privacy Guaranteed</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
